      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings have been addressed, ensuring structural integrity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise shift gates, transferring torque through a GKN-sourced variable M differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-tuned kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the signature communicative steering feel this platform is known for. While the exterior shows honest patina, the mechanical vitals are synchronized for peak performance.",
